          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Discourage Dishonest Dialing Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Communications Commission to establish regulations requiring providers of voice services to implement caller-identification information-authentication technology that can:</p> <ul> <li>verify that caller-identification information transmitted with a call is accurate, and </li> <li>alert a subscriber&nbsp;if a call cannot be verified.<br /></li></ul>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-09-13T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
